
"smart_sources:RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/pin/教辅/高中数学公式大全.md": {"path":"RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/pin/教辅/高中数学公式大全.md","last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"last_read":{"hash":"l6zcn5","at":1769676327825},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1768980884000,"size":181246,"at":1769676327834,"hash":"l6zcn5"},"blocks":{"#":[1,2966],"##{1}":[1,1],"##{2}":[4,4],"##{3}":[5,1766],"##{4}":[1767,1875],"##{5}":[1876,2039],"##{6}":[2040,2143],"##{7}":[2144,2228],"##{8}":[2229,2285],"##{9}":[2286,2308],"##{10}":[2309,2431],"##{11}":[2432,2518],"##{12}":[2519,2561],"##{13}":[2562,2594],"##{14}":[2595,2595],"##{15}":[2596,2610],"##{16}":[2611,2641],"##{17}":[2642,2652],"##{18}":[2653,2679],"##{19}":[2680,2697],"##{20}":[2698,2711],"##{21}":[2712,2731],"##{22}":[2732,2759],"##{23}":[2760,2770],"##{24}":[2771,2817],"##{25}":[2818,2830],"##{26}":[2831,2856],"##{27}":[2857,2865],"##{28}":[2866,2899],"##{29}":[2900,2908],"##{30}":[2909,2939],"##{31}":[2940,2945],"##{32}":[2946,2947],"##{33}":[2948,2958],"##{34}":[2959,2961],"##{35}":[2962,2966]},"outlinks":[{"title":"高中数学公式大全 电子版本","target":"../../高中数学公式大全 电子版本.md","line":4},{"title":"承白","target":"../../承白.md","line":5},{"title":"垂径定理","target":"../../垂径定理.md","line":221},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":1773},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":1780},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":1783},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":1882},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":1886},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":1888},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":1890},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":2045},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":2047},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":2150},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":2152},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":2154},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":2157},{"title":"a,+\\infty)$ ．\n        - 渐近线：$y= \\pm \\frac{b}{a} x$ ；离心率：$e=\\frac{c}{a}$\n        - 注意：若渐近线方程为 $y= \\pm \\frac{b}{a} x \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{x}{a} \\pm \\frac{y}{b}=0 \\Rightarrow$ 双曲线可设为 $\\frac{x^{2}}{a^{2}}-\\frac{y^{2}}{b^{2}}=\\lambda$\n        - 若双曲线与 $\\frac{x^{2}}{a^{2}}-\\frac{y^{2}}{b^{2}}=1$ 有公共渐近线，可设为 $\\frac{x^{2}}{a^{2}}-\\frac{y^{2}}{b^{2}}=\\lambda(\\lambda>0$ ，焦点在 $x$ 轴上，$\\lambda<0$ ，焦点在 $y$ 轴上）．\n    - \n    - 15，抛物线的定义：平面内到一个定点 $F$ 和到一条定直线 $l$（ $F$ 不在 $l$ 上）距离相等的点的轨迹．\n        - （1）焦点在 $x$ 轴的扡物线的标准方程：y^2^=a x ，焦点为 $\\left(\\frac{a}{4}, 0\\right)$ ，准线为 $x=-\\frac{a}{4}$ ，焦点到准线的距离为 $\\left|\\frac{a}{2}\\right|$ ，顶点为原点，关于 $x$ 轴对称．\n        - （2）焦点在 $y$ 轴的扡物线的标准方程：$x2=a y$ ，焦点为 $\\left(0, \\frac{a}{4}\\right)$ ，准线为 $y=-\\frac{a}{4}$ ，焦点到准线的距离为 $\\left|\\frac{a}{2}\\right|$ ，顶点为原点，关于 $y$ 轴对称．\n    - \n    - 16，直线与椭圆双曲线抛物线相交问题：设直线 $y=k x+b$ ，（过 x 轴上一点的直线有时可设为 $x=m y+t$ ）联立，消元，判别式，韦达定理。如果直线过抛物线焦点，关注扡物线上点到焦点距离与到准线距离的转化。\n        - \n        - \n\n          $$a x^{2}+b x+c=0\\left(a_{1} y^{2}+b_{1} y+c_{1}=0\\right) \\Rightarrow$$\n\n          \n        - \n    - \n    - （1）弦长：\n    - $|A B|=$ $\\qquad$ $=$ $\\qquad$\n    - ![","target":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/wT3uNkYxezt5Vqjk67tPBhVc-z1iI0ilVYjx8IjS_AL4mieiM63WnOwhT9xHgNRGR_8gQQl61YKgxIEPGZjpfQE6qo-GxZtsW4pK8qfbIOLBx1mtx65WbjvFa0R7hQ-k.jpeg","line":2404},{"title":"等轴双曲线","target":"../../等轴双曲线.md","line":2742}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},
